<h2>Chapter 5: Should You Block AI Crawlers? A Decision Framework &#123;#chapter-5&#125;</h2>
<p>The answer depends on your business model. Blocking everything sacrifices AI search visibility. Allowing everything gives away your content for free. The right approach sits in between.</p>
